script = ExtResource("1_qqioi")
release_version = "v1.3.1 (CM37E)"
notes = "[TITLE]Cog Creator 
Added the ability to add 20 different fixed proxy effects to the Cog Creator (Only one of each, though.)
Renamed the math version of Pop Quiz to 'Math Quiz'.
All cog types now have a single list of attacks in the Cog Creator (Do note, however, that some attacks will not animate for some cog types)
[TITLE]Balance Changes
Pilot Cap: Four Stars/Q6 -> Three Stars/Q5  
Grey Dots Boots: -15% Luck -> -10% Luck, Four Stars/Q4 -> Four Stars/Q5
[TITLE]Bug Fixes
Fixed the skulls being able to unfairly damage you while stunned during the Solicitor Boss Battle
The Big Skull Room will now play different music depending on whether or not its in the Frozen or Normal D.A. Office.
[TITLE] Hotfix #1
Partner Toons can now have more than just their first names! You can have a name like 'Captain Banjo Fuzzyflip'!"
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
